Sunday I woke up around 930 and went to the Knick game with my brother.  It was so sweet, we had awesome seats and they won.  NOw I have to finish chem and write my english essay.

nOBODY rEADS THESE BUT W.E

Im supposed to be an accountant :/   Went to school, that was fun...?, came home and played some SAN ANDREAS, then reffed a couple of bball games, fun stuff, but I didnt get to see the GANGSTER KID.  Probably going to the movies in an hour so peace.  And I just ate a cookie, mmmm cookie.

Today was ok. I chilled in school for a bit then left, then I got a haircut. Got a pretty big chem quiz tommorow, so Im going to study.
